                    <img src="~/Content/Images/community-lunch.jpg" alt="Community lunch">
                    <div class="news-content">
                        <h3>Do not miss the community lunch!</h3>
                        <p>Join us on the <strong>15th&nbsp;of&nbsp;July</strong>.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-more">Click for more →</a>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <br />
